query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(k mk t mi) */ select count(*)
from keyword AS k
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword ilike '%love%'
inner join title AS t
on mk.movie_id = t.id
inner join movie_info AS mi
on mi.movie_id = t.id AND mi.info ilike '%romance%'
inner join info_type AS it
on it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.id = 3;
